<item>
            <title>[LU-1907] Remove function resolution mistakes made by Coverity</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1907</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Coverity tool found some false out-of-bound access errors in the Lustre code. These false positives are due to bad function resolutions made by Coverity. The verification of such mistakes takes quite a long time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In order to quiet future Coverity runs, I will propose a patch that comments and annotates those false positives in the Lustre code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
